---
title: Sunsoaked Scrambled Egg Tacos Serves 2 | Mornings taste better with warm tortillas & avocados
description: Pour the mimosas because it's time for brunch. Warm tortillas, avocado salsa and soft, tasty cheesy scrambled eggs await you at this morning's breakfast table! Mix, match and dive in!
